Package org.jdrupes.httpcodec.protocols.http.fields

Classes that represent fields in HTTP headers.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HttpContentLengthField
    A specialization of HttpIntField that represents the content-length.
    HttpCookieListField
    The cookies representation.
    HttpDateField  
    HttpDateTimeField
    An HTTP Date/Time field as specified by RFC 7231, Section 7.1.1.1
    HttpField<T>
    A base class for all kinds of header field values.
    HttpIntField
    An HTTP field value that is an integer.
    HttpIntListField
    An HTTP field value that consists of a comma separated list of integers.
    HttpListField<T>
    An HTTP field value that consists of a list of separated by a delimiter strings.
    HttpMediaTypeField
    Represents a media type header field and provides methods for interpreting its value.
    HttpSetCookieListField
    Represents all “Set-Cookie” fields in a Response header.
    HttpStringField
    Represents a header field that has a simple string as its value.
    HttpStringListField
    An HTTP field value that consists of a comma separated list of strings.
    HttpUnquotedStringField
    Represents a header field that has a simple string as its value.
